snippet.title: Children's Museum Pretend City Fun! Kids and Family Indoor Outdoor Play Learning Activities
snippet.description:
It's ETHAN'S FUN TIME!  Join Ethan at the Children's Museum Pretend City where there are so many fun activities and learning toys!  There is a grocery store for kids filled with fruits and vegetables and all of the groceries you would find in a real grocery store!  There is even shopping lists and a checkouts with a cash register.  This Children's Museum Pretend City featured a full kids art studio, a pretend animal hospital and an outdoor water play area where you can float boats and spray water!  They even had science areas where you could shoot air pressure rockets or learn about molecules and magnets.  Ethan especially loved stomping on the bugs video game.  This is a fun kids video for children who loves playing at Children's Museums and Pretend Cities and loves learning new things with fun activities and toys!  We love making family fun videos!

snippet.title: Langdi Taang | बच्चों के खेल | Indian Games For Kids | Outdoor Games For Kids | Jalebi Street
snippet.description:
Hi kids, come join the Jalebi Gang as they learn a new Indian outdoor game for kids, the traditional Indian Game - Langdi Taang. Your kids will laugh with Bunny as he learns why playing outdoors is important, and they will run around with Bubble as she teaches her friends a new Indian traditional game she learned - The One Leg Hop. The kids make 2 teams and have a delightful time playing their new fun outdoor game. Come play outdoors with the Jalebi Street Gang and learn the traditional Langdi game.
Jalebi street pe Bubble aur uske doston ke sath seekhiye बच्चों के खेल. Bubble ne aaj naya Bhartiya khel seekha hai jiska naam hai लंगड़ी का खेल, aur woh apne doston ko yeh khel sikha rahi hai, to aap bhi Bubble ke sath yeh langadi game enjoy kar sakte hain.
